#: src/Admin/SettingsPage.php:133
msgid ""
"WWU Withdrawal Button — a free open-source compliance tool by %s, with "
"mredodos and Matteo Alfieri (An Idea for Business)."
msgstr "WWU Withdrawal Button — ett gratis open source-verktyg för regelefterlevnad av %s, med mredodos och Matteo Alfieri (An Idea for Business)."

#: src/Admin/SettingsPage.php:158
